reviews.text: Definitely visit this shop if you're in the area. Hands down one of the best Vietnamese/ Thai restaurants here. Prices are very reasonable. They serve lunch sets and there are hotpots in the evening. They make very good Tom Yum Goong. The location is a bit out of the way right now, but worth the trip. There is also delivery via deliveroo and foodpanda.
A really nice surprise, a small cosy venue that had a good number of restaurants in spite of the fact it's not directly accessible to the main road. Good food, pleasant staff, a good place...
Good food, Vietnamese owner
